                min) inside of an MC is well correlated with the intensity of geomagnetic activity, Dstmin (minimum Dst found within a storm event) for MCs (with a Pearson correlation coefficient,                                                                           $\mathrm{c.c.} =0.75$
                , and the fitting function is Dstmin=0.90+7.78Bz
